        "field_label": "Spa Market Class",
        "selection_rule": "Single-select",
        "field_description": "Comparison context for the establishment. Market Class does not determine rating, verification, price, or quality by itself. Price alone never determines class. Philippine internal planning reference (typical standard 60-minute individual massage): S usually PHP 2,500 or more; A usually PHP 1,500 to 2,499; B usually PHP 700 to 1,499; C usually PHP 350 to 699; D usually below PHP 350 or primarily short basic services. Other markets require locally reviewed thresholds.",
        "field_option": [
            {
                "option_code": "S",
                "option_label": "Luxury",
                "option_description": "Elite, highly refined spa experience with substantial premium facilities, privacy, service flow, and presentation."
